<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">“日出江花红胜火，春来江水绿如蓝”，生机勃勃的春天，鸟语花香的春天，一幅幅美如画的景象出现在我们的面前。为丰富校园文化生活，提升我院学子的审美情趣，展现我院师生与花朵之间的和谐之美，传递自然与人文的交融之情，经济管理学院开展“花间仙子，镜映自然”主题摄影比赛！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 20px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240411/1712836316955072123.png" title="1712836316955072123.png" alt="image.png" width="399" height="336" style="width: 399px; height: 336px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;">B230505潘舒灵 出镜&amp;摄</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 20px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240411/1712836371155047908.png" title="1712836371155047908.png" alt="image.png" width="394" height="334" style="width: 394px; height: 334px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B220510陈彦曦 出镜&amp;摄</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 20px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240411/1712836411083043761.png" title="1712836411083043761.png" alt="image.png" width="399" height="369" style="width: 399px; height: 369px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B220503何舒静 出镜&amp;摄</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 20px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240411/1712836453367055922.png" title="1712836453367055922.png" alt="image.png" width="406" height="355" style="width: 406px; heigh